    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:8px;"><text style="font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold;">Servomotor Coupling</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">The motor shaft and the ball screw are connected by a motor coupling. The coupling consists of a coupling flange and flat spring. The coupling flange is deformed when the clamping screws are tightened and the motor shaft and ball screw are connected by means of frictional force.</para>
